metaResult.name: Lacunar Leech
metaResult.description:
A parasitic worm that feeds on Voidmatter and anything else unlucky enough to stand between it and a meal.
Lacunar Leeches are the only known organism to produce Saalt; a rare mineral that can be used to induce a trance-like state.

metaResult.name: Grim #160
metaResult.description: The Grim Syndicate is a collection of 10,000 generated Grims that do the dirty work of playing afterlife janitors across all planes of existence; in fetching those stubborn Souls who vacate their living vessels but aren’t ready to move on to the Ethereal Realm. What you call a haunting, these Reaper Agents call “all in a day’s work”.

metaResult.name: Monkey Paw
metaResult.description:
A withered limb seldom found in the murky tombs of the Knownverse. Adjacent runic texts touch upon an ancient yet oddly familiar species.
Rumored to curse travellers with maddening authority, its appendages slither at the touch of those yearning for more.
